{
  "stem": "1965.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we can absolutely bring ourselves into communication to make it better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I would like to share with you, Sontha, an experience during the course of the prewar.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When the war had begun, we were still living at a place known as [NON-ENGLISH], Antwerpen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We lived on the third floor-- no elevator.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the third floor was almost like six floors here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had two rooms and a toilet on the outside, in the hallway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one night, we heard very loud banging at the front door downstairs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we all were like, trembling, you know, because we knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had heard the sirens, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the Gestapo came upstairs, forcefully knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they told my father to get ready in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Unless you go through this, to see your father being taken away for no reason at all, but just to be taken away-- my mother became hysterical.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was a nervous wreck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She developed Crohn disease, bleeding ulcers, and she could not concentrate and help no more her three children because of her illnesses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She had six major operations during her lifetime.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were then brought-- because my mother was taken to a hospital-- and we, the three children, were then taken away from that domicile.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was six to six and 1/2, if I-- I think I was closer to six than six and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was born in '36, so we're talking anywhere-- the latter part of '42.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I will say this-- that when you hear the constant sirens and the bombs, you who are standing there in your domicile, you have no-- you-- you don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're totally, completely powerless.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
